ram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 679}, {\"ngram\": \"her true sexuality\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 731}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"humiliating\\\" interrogations\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 791}, {\"ngram\": \"base\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 811}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discussing the interrogations that saw her belongings dashed across the room, Holmes shared: \\\"It was really difficult because there was interrogation that happened.\", \"from\": 814, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 892, \"end\": 898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"score\": 0.9999999693823161, \"rank\": 3.061771696395839e-08, \"text\": \"Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the interrogations\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"her belongings\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 867}, {\"ngram\": \"the room\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 890}, {\"ngram\": \"interrogation\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the documentary, I explain it a lot and I speak to people that dealt with some shocking things, but for me personally, having raids, it was scary, humiliating, embarrassing.\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 1155, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the documentary\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1039}, {\"ngram\": \"some shocking things\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1076}, {\"ngram\": \"raids\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"People were tipped off, the Royal Military Police would come into your barracks and literally turn everything upside down, take everything out, you'd be left with your belongings lying around.\", \"from\": 1157, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1207, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Royal_Military_Police\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6442711614836836e-32