: 0.9999999693823161, \"rank\": 3.061771696395839e-08, \"text\": \"Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\"}, {\"begin\": 1819, \"end\": 1830, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loose_Women\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.558318032981684e-45, \"text\": \"Loose Women\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loose_Women\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Loose_Women\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the documentary\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1638}, {\"ngram\": \"then-Prime ministerRishi\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"behalf\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1690}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1708}, {\"ngram\": \"other gay soldiers\", \"from\": 1729, \"to\": 1747}, {\"ngram\": \"the former athlete\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"the apology\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"the toll\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"her mental health\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"her sexuality\", \"from\": 1904, \"to\": 1917}, {\"ngram\": \"the army\", \"from\": 1921, \"to\": 1929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was raided.\", \"from\": 1932, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The royal military police would come into my private space, my bedroom, and ransack it completely, be intimidating, interrogating, be in my face.\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 2092, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The royal military police\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"my private space\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2005}, {\"ngram\": \"my bedroom\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2017}, {\"ngram\": \"my face\", \"from\": 2084, \"to\": 2091}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was scared.\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was 23.\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2116, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was petrified.\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2133, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not want to lose my career.\", \"from\": 2134, \"to\": 2167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me personally that caused me mental health issues throughout my whole career.\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my whole career\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2248}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was so petrified as the shame was institutionally driven into me, hence why I did not come out until last year.\\\"\", \"from\": 2250, \"to\": 2364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shame\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2281}, {\"ngram\": \"last year\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2362}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was only in June 2022 when the Pembury native publicly came out during an exclusive interview with theSunday Mirroras she expressed her delight in being able to announce the news on her own terms.\", \"from\": 2368, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 2383, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"the Pembury native\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"an exclusive interview\", \"from\": 2442, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"theSunday Mirroras\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2488}, {\"ngram\": \"her delight\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"the news\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2549}, {\"ngram\": \"her own terms\", \"from\": 2553, \"to\": 2566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I needed to do this now, for me,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2568, \"to\": 2612, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was my decision.\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2633, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my decision\", \"from\": 2621, \"to\": 2632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am nervous about saying it.\", \"from\": 2634, \"to\": 2663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel like I am going to explode with excitement.\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2714, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes I cry with relief.\", \"from\": 2715, \"to\": 2743, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"relief\", \"from\": 2736, \"to\": 2742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The moment this comes out, I am essentially getting rid of that fear.\\\"\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2814, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that fear\", \"from\": 2803, \"to\": 2812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Holmes revealed the moment she realised she was gay after sharing a kiss with a fellow soldier at a bathroom block.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2816, \"end\": 2822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"score\": 0.9999999693823161, \"rank\": 3.061771696395839e-08, \"text\": \"Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2832, \"to\": 2842}, {\"ngram\": \"a kiss\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2888}, {\"ngram\": \"a fellow soldier\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2910}, {\"ngram\": \"a bathroom block\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2930}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I realised I must be gay then because it felt good.\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It felt more natural, I felt comfortable,\\\" she recalled.\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having admitted to being involved in secret relationships with other female soldiers, she was well aware of the consequences that would befall her should she have gotten caught.\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3219, \"entiti